        <odd id="ref74">
            <head>Early American History Note</head>
            <p>Written in Latin, this essay on natural philosophy written by Pennsylvania minister David Evans in 1747 reflects his broad knowledge of natural history. Please see the entire MOLE entry for a more detailed summary of the volume's content.</p>
